     FAH#PW40 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     FAH#TL11 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAH#PP11 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAH#WP40 O   F     100            DISK
     E                    HBM         3  4 0             ﾎﾞy]ﾃｰnﾞ
     E                    MSG     1   5 60               d[ｰxｮﾈｰﾆﾞ
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80CFSKHZ
     I                                        1   40CFSKYY
     I                                        5   60CFSKMM
     I                                        7   80CFSKDD
